'Created by Peter Horsbøll Møller, Precisely
'Parameters:
'
'**********************************************************************************************''
Function ERRGetLatestErrorNo() As Integer

OnError GoTo ErrorOccured

	ERRGetLatestErrorNo	= ERRGetErrorNo(mnNumErrors)
